{"tid":617750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"衣食住行 邊樣最捨得用錢?","createTime":"2018-04-05T08:26:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T09:01:32.000Z","uid":157128,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"703fd520a940e396059ac4760551d81f38f45f32","tid":617750,"uid":157128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T08:26:03.000Z","msg":"衣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人靠衣裝,衣著可以表現自己<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 靚仔著U記都靚,舒服抵著就得<br />\n<br />\n食<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食落肚係享受,對身體好啲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果腹,快餐無問題,最後都係變屎<br />\n<br />\n住<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 生活品質,每日每晚起居嘅地方<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 皇帝都係訓張床<br />\n<br />\n行<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去到目的地,地鐵巴士都Ok,價錢平,環保<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 揸車自由,方便,唔使同其他人迫<br />\n<br />\n以下為真實例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買潮牌捱麵包<br />\n食貴嘢住劏房<br />\n住靚樓但飲食衣着好樸素<br />\n無錢食飯人工得十幾廿K都要養車<br />\n<br />\n你又會點揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我: 住第一, 行包尾, 衣食中間"},{"pid":"0f1676a3216dfc3cb97464535a9660249f6f5ff3","tid":617750,"uid":34714,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T08:27:20.000Z","msg":"行果度調轉左!"},{"pid":"77c70e2960982e2a12ae3ac03291016189ee02d9","tid":617750,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T08:27:43.000Z","msg":"首先要有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38f3280d0c32ffbff738808b7d5fe1575ea0cfcf","tid":617750,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-0